casebody.data:
John Neilans, Respondent, v. Charles Stanton and Others, Appellants.

Order affirmed, with ten dollars costs and disbursements. All concur. (The order denies a motion for a change of venue in an action for damages for false arrest and malicious prosecution.)

Present — Sears, P. J., Crosby, Lewis, Taylor and Dowling, JJ.
